SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.stanje_promet = 'Z') AND (acdt_o.strokovni_pregled >= 2.99) AND (acdt_o.strokovni_pregled < 10.05) AND (acdt_o.alkotest < 9.54);
select count(*) from nesreca as acdt_n, oseba as acdt_o, upravna_enota as acdt_ue where acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota = acdt_n.upravna_enota and acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota and acdt_o.vozniski_staz_mm = 1 and acdt_n.stanje_promet = 'G' and acdt_o.vrsta_udelezenca = 'OA';
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.stanje_promet = 'G') AND (acdt_o.starost >= 47) AND (acdt_o.starost < 82) AND (acdt_o.vozniski_staz_mm = 3);
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_o.starost >= 72) AND (acdt_o.vozniski_staz_mm = 3) AND (acdt_o.alkotest_d = 'B') AND (acdt_o.spol = '2');
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o, upravna_enota acdt_ue WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.naselje_ali_izven = 'D') AND (acdt_o.vozniski_staz_mm = 5) AND (acdt_o.poskodba = 'U');
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.vreme_nesreca = 'J') AND (acdt_n.stanje_promet = 'N') AND (acdt_o.alkotest < 8.16) AND (acdt_o.varnostni_pas_ali_celada = '1');
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o, upravna_enota acdt_ue WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.klas_nesreca = 'B') AND (acdt_o.starost < 63) AND (acdt_o.starost_d = 'G');
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_n.kategorija_cesta = '3') AND (acdt_n.stanje_vozisce = 'SL') AND (acdt_n.stanje_povrsina_vozisce = 'A') AND (acdt_o.starost_d = 'D');
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM nesreca acdt_n, oseba acdt_o WHERE (acdt_n.upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota) AND (acdt_o.alkotest >= 2.47) AND (acdt_o.starost >= 32) AND (acdt_o.starost < 58) AND (acdt_o.vozniski_staz_mm = 11);
select count(*) from nesreca as acdt_n, oseba as acdt_o, upravna_enota as acdt_ue where acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota = acdt_n.upravna_enota and acdt_ue.id_upravna_enota = acdt_o.upravna_enota and acdt_o.starost_d = 'C' and acdt_n.vreme_nesreca = 'M' and acdt_o.vrsta_udelezenca = 'TV';
